Senator Natasha Akpoti-Uduaghan drags Godswill  Akpabio to Deutsche Welle News, Germany.

From AriseNews in Nigeria to the Inter Parliamentary Union, IPU in Geneva, Switzerland, to BBC and Sky News in London, Natasha whose last word before she was led out of the Senate Chamber was, "This Injustice Will Not Be Sustained," has vowed to drag Akpabio in the mud. 
